cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you reference the AI Usage Scale, please cite it as below."
title: "The AI Usage Scale"
abstract: >-
  An open, six-level standard for declaring how a work was made with generative AI —
  whose substance it carries, and whether a person reviewed it before publication.
  Human-readable and machine-readable, CC0, interoperable with IPTC, C2PA and the W3C
  AI Content Disclosure work. No level ranks above another.
type: software
authors:
